&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Reconciliation:&lt;/strong&gt; Conduct bank and credit card reconciliations, monitor cash flow, and maintain accurate account balances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accounts Payable/Receivable:&lt;/strong&gt; Manage vendor onboarding, payments, invoicing support, and tracking of client payments.&lt;/li&gt;
